The paper discusses the need for digital forensics in the context of IoT and WSNs, which are both related to computer security (cs.CR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses technical challenges and future research opportunities, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE), cyber security (cs.CY), and distributed computing (cs.DC).
